o/workspace --yes assess verify --snapshot snapshot_demo_0001\r\nSnapshot snapshot_demo_0001: supported\r\n\r\nFinding finding_demo_0001\r\nTarget claim: claim_demo_0001\r\nStatus: supported\r\nReason: The Vera Example claim resolves to the supplied fact, evidence-item, and raw-log closure.\r\nUnsupported phrases:\r\n- none\r\nCounterevidence:\r\n- none\r\n\r\nFinding finding_demo_0002\r\nTarget claim: claim_demo_0002\r\nStatus: supported\r\nReason: The Vera Example claim resolves to the supplied fact, evidence-item, and raw-log closure.\r\nUnsupported phrases:\r\n- none\r\nCounterevidence:\r\n- none\r\n\r\n$ exp2res --workspace demo/workspace assess show --snapshot snapshot_demo_0001\r\nSelf-Assessment — Global\r\nclaim_demo_0001\tpattern_signal\tworking_style\tmedium\tsupported\r\nclaim_demo_0002\tnarrative_summary\ttrajectory\tmedium\tsupported\r\n\r\n$ exp2res --workspace demo/workspace export assessment --snapshot snapshot_demo_0001\r\ndemo/workspace/out/assessment/snapshot_demo_0001/manifest.json\r\ndemo/workspace/out/assessment/snapshot_demo_0001/evidence_map.json\r\ndemo/workspace/out/assessment/snapshot_demo_0001/report.md\r\ndemo/workspace/out/assessment/snapshot_demo_0001/self_claims.json\r\n\r\nClaim claim_demo_0001 -> fact fact_demo_0001 -> evidence evi_demo_0001 -> raw log log_demo_0001\r\n\r\n$ exp2res --workspace demo/workspace logs show --log-id log_demo_0001\r\n{\r\n  \"log\": {\r\n    \"id\": \"log_demo_0001\",\r\n    \"recorded_at\": \"2026-06-02T21:00:00+02:00\",\r\n    \"entry_type\": \"manual_daily\",\r\n    \"source_type\": \"manual_entry\",\r\n    \"occurred\": {\r\n      \"start\": \"2026-06-02T00:00:00+02:00\",\r\n      \"end\": null,\r\n      \"precision\": \"exact_day\",\r\n      \"confidence\": \"high\"\r\n    },\r\n    \"project\": \"K8s Playbook\",\r\n    \"corrects_log_id\": null,\r\n    \"external_ref\": \"examples/vera/corpus/logs/daily-2026-06-02.md\"\r\n  },\r\n  \"evidence_items\": [\r\n    {\r\n      \"id\": \"evi_demo_0001\",\